{"tid":1537804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"吳明德教授 中共內鬥 越亂越好","createTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:31.000Z","uid":92989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"edfca6a6c7ec516aa6dec42c0a322f6c8247fbb2","tid":1537804,"uid":92989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=pqzKQnmq0Cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DpqzKQnmq0Cs&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3GWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=637c229c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=pqzKQnmq0Cs</a><br />\n<br />\n最近班狗越黎越惡，刻意製造混亂，主要原因係想迫習大大岀兵。原本習派想通過逃犯條例迫死江派，但係習派諗吾到反應咁大。而習大大之前都亦留意到市民係好和平。而江派（中聯辦及港澳辦）就利用過去都係由江派控制既黑警，今次目的係要香港市民一齊癲，迫習派岀解放軍，令經濟 人道主義 入曬佢數迫佢問責落台。我地香港人依家成為一隻權鬥棋子。我地應該好好保護自己，留得青山在那怕無柴燒。<br />\n<br />\n聽人講香港人權及民主法案制裁名單，好似又真係大部分都係中聯辦及港澳辦既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef325cedbc1468a4f2b85d9582cd9a26c273281","tid":1537804,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}